    hospitalSystemsPara: "NewYork-Presbyterian, Mount Sinai Health System, NYU Langone, and Montefiore dominate Manhattan and the Bronx, while Northwell Health covers much of Queens, Nassau, and Suffolk. NYC Health + Hospitals operates 11 public hospitals including Bellevue, Elmhurst, and Kings County that serve as the safety net for uninsured and Medicaid patients. Consolidation between NYU Langone and Winthrop on Long Island has reduced competitive pricing pressure in the eastern borough corridor.",
